title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show AUG-19-2013 MON
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show AUG-19-2013 MON






The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET




Glenn and the guys discuss the situation over in Egypt 
  and how the chaos will eventually affect us.

 Also talks about the new, "For The Record" coming up on the Blaze this Thursday night.

 And the father of the 8th Grade boy molested in Michigan joins Glenn to share his story.

 Also discusses the upcoming debut of Al Jazeera America and the Million Muslim March....
